{"tid":265010,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[敗家劇]蘭花劫首播收視跌破20點 流失43萬觀眾","createTime":"2017-05-31T10:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T08:39:53.000Z","uid":65144,"like":100,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d087edb7fdc108c26ff4084a53788087414c5b3","tid":265010,"uid":65144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:08:38.000Z","msg":"TVB播映10年前倉底劇《蘭花刼》，低清畫質成熱話，有網民形容似睇粵語長片，TVB挑戰觀眾的底線，收視成績反映觀眾接受程度。《蘭花刼》首集平均收視19.3、最高20.4(觀眾人數132萬6千)。第二集平均18.2，最高19點(觀眾人數約123萬5千)，周一至五的黃金時間收視跌破2字頭，在低收視紀錄留名。 <br />\n<br />\n《蘭花刼》接4K製作的《不懂撒嬌的女人》棒播映，《撒嬌》贏口碑賺收視，上周一至五的平均收視24.9。觀眾由睇4K製作，突然時光倒流10年睇標清製作，落差太大難適應。以對上一星期《撒嬌》的平均24.9收視跟前晚《蘭花刼》的平均18.2比較，流失觀眾達43萬。討論區有網民指TVB的高層安排10年前的《蘭花刼》在黃金時間播映，認為恃一台獨大以觀眾做籌碼。今次《蘭花刼》第一、二集的收視成績，輸了43萬觀眾，認真敗家!<br />\n(即時娛樂)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1496216590590&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20170531\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1496216590590%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20170531&d=UKJ7iNP0vuxfX4FTDXyrgRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=3e855cb2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1496216590590%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20170531&h=7f632f11\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1496216590590&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20170531</a>"},{"pid":"ba712681f040855e257fd008194e549d9077d763","tid":265010,"uid":65144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:09:28.000Z","msg":"tvb d打手落力d推啦，扣你人工架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a790a1472ad9fe47fe2b730968b3450e8fd5695","tid":265010,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:10:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5448c42100e89e3b870f5473508128bad4b83cc","tid":265010,"uid":85819,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyT